# Copy to .env and set one key for your llm_model (see LiteLLM docs for provider env names).
# Already-set shell variables take precedence over this file (override=False in monad.py).
#
#   cp .env.example .env

# Examples (uncomment one):
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# GEMINI_API_KEY=
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=